column1: # Readings for the following periods are apportioned:
# The following readings are estimates and have been omitted:
# The readings January-March 1947 are estimated for snow and have been retained.
# The reading for May 1947 is part-estimated and has been retained.
# The reading for October 1950 is part-estimated and has been retained.
# The reading for December 1955 is part-estimated and has been retained.
# The reading for October 1956 is part-estimated and has been retained.
# The 1950s sheet gives the location as Round Crag.
# The station is still active according to MIDAS.
